    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Piece by Piece</i>是一款真正意义上的益智平台游戏，每个关卡都被分割成不同的拼图碎片，通过将这些碎片缝合在一起（<i>一块接一块</i>）来探索关卡。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >游戏包含100个精心设计的关卡，难度会不断提升，并配有多种独特机制。轻松却又引人入胜的氛围，让<i>Piece by Piece</i>非常适合喜欢新颖挑战的解谜和平台游戏玩家。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/221c4d81a33087d5602e588465377714.poster.avif?t=1772147762\" width=1170 height=448 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/221c4d81a33087d5602e588465377714.webm?t=1772147762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/221c4d81a33087d5602e588465377714.mp4?t=1772147762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个主题都加入了全新的机制，让你在一个又一个关卡盒子中不断测试逻辑思维。传送门、挖掘、旋转碎片以及更多惊喜等待发现！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/b32181ef73765b2a33509acce507936f.poster.avif?t=1772147762\" width=1170 height=444 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/b32181ef73765b2a33509acce507936f.webm?t=1772147762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/b32181ef73765b2a33509acce507936f.mp4?t=1772147762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >混合关卡将不同主题和机制融为一体，考验你对每项新元素的掌握。你能通关全部100个关卡吗？别忘记每关都要收集那块金色拼图哦！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/b0ceac53b87e0338cdc205ad03606cf1.poster.avif?t=1772147762\" width=1170 height=354 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/b0ceac53b87e0338cdc205ad03606cf1.webm?t=1772147762\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3249380/extras/b0ceac53b87e0338cdc205ad03606cf1.mp4?t=1772147762\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
